name: Refactoring in Ruby
description:
Last month, we explored how to test drive our Ruby. Now it's time for the next step.

Join Micah Cooper and gain confidence and comfort when improving your codebase with the help of some good test coverage and an a curious attitude towards the Ruby and Rails documentation.

name: Ruby Tuesday - RubyJax OpenHacks
description: Come hang out at Starbucks and work on some code. Bring your projects or come for help, all levels welcome.
